Introduction

Dani is a British singer and rapper under FrontRow Records. She is a former member and rapper of the London-based girl group KAACHI. Prior to joining KAACHI, Dani was a member of the London-based Kpop dance cover group, UJJN, along with fellow KAACHI members Nicole and Chunseo.
